    <h1 class="title-case-study">Activate Learning</h1>

    <div class="collage-text formatting">
      <div class="grid-2">
        <p>The reality of education technology never quite lives up to expectations. Devices in classrooms may lead to savvier pupils, but do these tools actually improve learning ability? Technology so often can focus on the rather unambitious path of incremental changes to already established practice. However, being dedicated to improving tools ignores key factors to meaningful change: teacher's pedagogy and student curiosity.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid-2">
        <p>When we first met the Verso team, we were inspired by their empathy towards education. This team of seasoned educators and technologists shared a vision to expand students propensity to learn. Whereas many edtech products optimize rote learning, Verso partnered with us to transform their immense classroom experience into a product that sparks curiosity.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

</header>

