  <div class="full-up formatting">
    <h2>Classroom IQ</h2>
    <p>None of this would be possible without buy-in from teachers. Verso’s interpretation of the flipped classroom model builds upon extensive research. Our challenge was to translate research-backed strategies into a action.</p>

    <p>Verso organically generates a wealth of usage data. We needed to be intelligent about shaping this data into actionable insights and  communicating it just-in-time. Teachers get realtime feedback on the lesson and can benchmark against past performance. Data-driven principals or department heads finally have a measurable way to identify what works.</p>
  </div>
